g.text: * when a user upvotes, an SNS publishes {userId, postId} to a vote-topic
* after a successful publish, a success response is returned
* one will increase the post's votes by pulling as many votes as possible
* the second queue will create a user-post-vote record
* posts are sorted by votes first and later by datetimes
* system is in micro service architecture with docker & docker compose
* frontend with NEXT.JS and typescript, hosted on AWS amplify
* database with MongoDB hosted on mongodb atlas, managed with compass
